  "detailed_description": "\"EYE TO ME\" is an adventure game set in the modern era.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Story<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am creating your \"video game.\"<br />\r\nI am showing \"it\" while eating fries at the store.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhy? How come?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"I just wanted a place where I could talk a little about my memories with you.\"<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI see, that sounds nice.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou stare at me with big eye.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEYE, EYE, EYE.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Game Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- A walking simulator where various events occur as you walk.<br />\r\n- Progress the story by examining objects.<br />\r\n- No quest markers or time limits, allowing for relaxed gameplay.<br />\r\n- A large \"eye\" is staring at me.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaytime: 10 to 30 minutes<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Streaming Guidelines<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Streaming is allowed without prior permission for both individuals and organizations.",
